{"tid":2381754,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[慶祝香港開埠第一百八十週年]  日本太空人拍攝香港全境","createTime":"2021-01-26T22:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T21:50:25.000Z","uid":251732,"like":70,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5670be070b83cc2e8f7d0e3d6b6f3701a7b05384","tid":2381754,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T22:58:28.000Z","msg":"我哋呢一個偉大嘅香港家國真係好撚靚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋真係好撚鍾意香港呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋唔係想走，而係呢個地方入面嘅畜生同屎忽鬼迫我哋冇得揀要離鄉別井<br />\n 但到最後人必有一死 ， 任何形式嘅強權必然會面對佢終結嘅一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而我哋必然會成為歷史的勝利者，並將我哋嘅鬥志傳承畀我哋嘅子子孫孫直到永遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efDzfGE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FefDzfGE.jpg&h=db490097&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">我們永不忘記 我們永不原諒<br />\n我們必定反抗 我們必定報仇<br />\n<br />\n我願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n沒有暴徒 只有暴政<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n剿滅匪類 刻不容緩<br />\n民族自強 香港獨立<br />\n香港人 建國<br />\n天滅中共 全黨死清光</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmuisoe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwmuisoe.gif&h=6bce165d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Astro_Soichi/status/1353975011392901120?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAstro_Soichi%2Fstatus%2F1353975011392901120%3Fs%3D19&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv1DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=e095758e\" data-ef